not_owner: You are not the owner of this vehicle
not_registered: This vehicle is not registered, couldn't spawn it
not_in_vehicle: You have to be in a vehicle to do this
not_in_parking_spot: You have to be at your parking spot, a waypoint has been set to it. Run /v park again at the spot to park your vehicle
no_parking_spot: You don't have a parking spot setup, run /v buy to buy a parking spot
no_access: You don't have access to this command
no_impounded_vehicles: You have no vehicles in the impound
menu_description_one: Take this vehicle out of storage.
menu_description_two: Place a marker at the current location of this vehicle.
successfully_added: Successfully added vehicle with model %s to player %s
successfully_deleted: Vehicle with plate number '%s' has been successfully deleted.
failed_to_save_parking: Failed to save the parking spot
failed_to_set_status: Failed to set the status of the vehicle
failed_to_set: Failed to set vehicle as owned
failed_to_spawn: Your vehicle is at the impound or it failed to spawn
failed_to_delete: Vehicle with plate number '%s' does not exist.
impound_description: Take this vehicle out of the impound lot.
invalid_model: That vehicle model does not seem to exist
invalid_format: You need to fill in all fields of the command in the following format /givevehicle [model] [targetId]
vehicle_doesnt_exist: Your vehicle does not exist, meaning it's in the impound

commands.givevehicle: Give a vehicle to another player
commands.deletevehicle: Delete a vehicle from a players storage
commands.impound: Send a vehicle to the impound lot.
